task.summary: Added test source folder and test resource folder.
Moved test classes to default package.
Added fixes tests from tail recursion.
Added type based initial value for ret variable and fixed a bug.
Removed dependency of project on test sources.
Changed all names to be suggested.
Added new test and some refactoring.
Added continue statement support and tests.
Now only statements containing recursive calls get separated in blocks.
Refactored return statements and now the stack is an ArrayDeque.
Fixed bug when trivial block with id 0 got removed (not good).
Fixed problem with multiple local variables sharing the same name.
Refined the algorithm for frame variables.
Backup commit (broken tests, but seems to do the right thing).
Forgot about this (should be added to the previous commit).
Added unreachable and trivial blocks removal.
Renamed concrete visitor to inline and deleted stupid NewBlocksGenerator.
